FBIS4-50674 "drchi098_j_94003" FBIS-CHI-94-098 Daily Report 14 May 1994 Latin America & Caribbean Exchanges Views With Chi Haotian Exchanges Views With Chi Haotian OW1405110094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0945 GMT 14 May 94 OW1405110094 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 14 (XINHUA) -- Chi Haotian, state councillor and minister of national defense, met with Jorge Lucar Figueroa, deputy commander-in-chief of Chilean Army, here today. During the meeting, the two sides exchanged views on furthering ties between the armed forces of the two countries as well as issues of common interests. Li Jing, deputy chief of general staff of the Chinese People's Liberation Army, was present.
